channel.title: Will the FUll source of 2006scape (RS 2006 . net) ever be leaked?
channel.description:
Not to be disrespectfull or anything, I just went throught their website, and i must admit they do a great job, but i was curious when the server is fixed( with all the skills and minigames(not the quests)) would there be a leak once so we can download it?, because i would love to get a better look on how rs were on the good days, but i aint wanna waste another 300 gameplay hours on getting my main some good combat and a 99 skill.
so u guys think it will ever get leaked??
